      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNBURNT KEEPER (1) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.36) in a Grade 5, finishing a 11 length fourth. With a clean break looks hard to beat. SANDRA KEEPING (5) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (31.05) at this track in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 5 for the first time. Expected to feature again. ZIPPING LYNDY (2) missed the frame latest when seventh at The Gardens (30.39) but scored five back at this track (30.79). Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Great chance to atone. BAGO SWEETIE (7) can sneak into the finish.",
